2 Data Source

Downloaded: December 10, 2014 directly from authors

Native Data Resolution:

Values: Count (number/km2) and weight (g/km2) across 4 size classes

Time Range: N/A

Format: GeoTIFF

3.2 Unlog data and crop to BC regions
